                    </p>
                    <p>&copy; GroupUpUTD</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-6 right-col">
                    <ul class="list-of-links">
                        <li>
                            <h2>Links</h2></li>
                        <li><a>UTD Health Center</a></li>
                        <li><a>Campus Counseling Center</a></li>
